headline.print_headline: Lopez Retains Eastbourne Title, Keys Wins Her 1st
headline.main: Lopez Retains Eastbourne Title, Keys Wins Her 1st

lead_paragraph: Feliciano Lopez of Spain completed a successful title defense when he beat top seed Richard Gasquet of France 6-3, 6-7 (5), 7-5 in the Aegon International final on Saturday.
